{
  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT can be a useful tool for beginning authors to learn the main writing principles and avoid making common mistakes.",
    "The ability of the chatbot to generate large amounts of text encourages the author to look for original solutions and distinctive details to include in the story.",
    "We also found that ChatGPT goodly emulates human writing manner, but not always from the perspective of sense.",
    "For editors there is a need to identify whether the text was created by AI or by human, so-called Turning Test.",
    "Several recently proposed neural network-based language models have demonstrated their astonishing capabilities to generate texts that are challenging to distinguish from human-written texts with the naked eye (Uchendu et al., 2020)."
  ]
}